name: Sunrise To Sunset - Digital Album
description: Track listing: 1. Heaven 2. From Sunrise To Sunset 3. Take This Life 4. Come Around 5. I Can Feel Your Love 6. Spirit Move 7. Resurrection *bonus track: Burrito Boy 8. Walking On Water (Surfah Girl) 9. Acoustic Rhymes 10. Thank You 5 out of 5 stars! "I watched Paul Wright play a concert on the beach in Panama City Beach, FL. He started playing as the sun was setting and we danced and listened to him sing for about an hour. Really his voice is awesome and just makes you want to get up and dance!" (San_Diego_Girl - itunes review)

name: Diego's Diary - Digital Album
description: Track listing: 1. 5th and Broadway 2. Pacific Beach (PB) 3. Ocean Beach 4. La Jolla 5. Chula Vista 6. Encinitas 7. Sunset Cliffs (Take Me Over) 8. Saratoga Springs 9. Torrey Pines High (Mind Games) 10. Carlsbad 11. OB Pier 12. Little Italy (She Says) 5 out of 5 stars! "As a frequent traveler to San Diego, I have, dare-I-say, fallen in love with the area. There's nothing more refreshing than the coloristic lifestyle that varies and defines the city and beaches. Paul Wright's music is no different. With his catchy hooks and renaissance-esque guitar style, you will soon find yourself singing along to his songs. More than that, these particular songs are tales depicted from a book that P. Wright is writing called "Diego's Diary". Hodad's has the best burgers, Paul Wright has the best music!" - hiphopchickin (itunes review)

name: Kingdom Come - Digital Album
description: Track listing: 1. Lost 2. Bring Me Back 3. Sing Your Name 4. Sorry 5. Judgement Comes 6. Don't Walk Be Her Door 7. Turn Me Around 8. All About You 9. Kingdom Come 10. Sing Your Name (acoustic) 5 out of 5 stars! "Great! Much more acoustic than previous albums but its just a natural thing for him to sing about his life. love it, LOVE it, LOVE IT!" (appolyonnicbelief - itunes review)

name: The Digital Collection
description:
Get all six of Paul's CDs in digital format for only $30 for a limited time!

Albums include:

Fly Away - Winter 2003
Sunrise to Sunset - Summer 2005
Wright or Wrong these songs are Paul's - Spring 2006
Kingdom Come - Fall 2007
Diego's Diary - Summer 2008

name: Valentines Custom Song!
description: Aloha friends!  It's that time of year again to treat your girlfriend, boyfriend, husband or wife to something special!  I am offering to write and record custom verses of your love story to an unreleased song.  Limited to the first ten customers.  After you order I will send you some questions to respond to and then I will record your song and email you a mp3 in time to give it to your honey!  Happy Valentines!
